                     </persName>
                  , widow, and 
                     <persName id="t17731208-24-person307">
                        Joseph
                         Croft
                     <interp inst="t17731208-24-person307" type="surname" value="Croft"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17731208-24-person307" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17731208-24-person307" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , on the <rs id="t17731208-24-cd120" type="crimeDate">28th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17731208-24-off119 t17731208-24-cd120"></join>, about the hour of eight in the night, and stealing four pair of silver salts, value 4 l. 16 s. two pair of plated salts, value 25 s. two silver milk pails, value 2 l. 12 s. three silver tops for castors, value 3 s. and a plated coffee pot, value 2 l. 10 s. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17731208-24-person308">
                        Bate
                         Trotman
                     <interp inst="t17731208-24-person308" type="surname" value="Trotman"></interp>
